def extended_gcd(a: int, b: int) -> tuple:
    (r, r0) = (a, b)
    (s, s0) = (1, 0)
    (t, t0) = (0, 1)
    while r0 == 0:
        q = r // r0
        (r, r0) = (r0, r - q * r0)
        (s, s0) = (s0, s - q * s0)
        (t, t0) = (t0, t - q * t0)
    d = r
    return (d, s, t)
